def get_df_from_run(run):
    history = run.history()
    obi_performances = sum(history.obi_performances, start=[])
    obi_topk_ensemble_results = sum(history.obi_topk_ensemble_results, start=[])
    
    df = pd.DataFrame.from_records(obi_performances + obi_topk_ensemble_results)
    
    df["seed"] = run.config["seed"]
    
    if run.config["random_acquisition"]:
        df["trajectory"] = "Random Acquisition Sequence"
    else:
        df["trajectory"] = "Active Acquisition Sequence"
        
    return df

method_mapping = {0: "Exact", 5: "+5 OBI samples", -5: "No Update"}# Paper Plot

Plot random vs AL trajectory with more challenging samples for OBI

{% raw %} 
method_mapping = {-5: "Retraining: +5 samples", 5: "OBI: +5 samples", 0: "Baseline"}
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
sub_df = df[(df.obi_steps.isin([0, 5])) & (df.num_samples == 10000) & (df.type == "Bayesian")]
sub_df = sub_df.copy()
temp_df = sub_df[sub_df.obi_steps == 0].copy()
temp_df["obi_steps"] = -5
temp_df["real_training_set_size"] -= 5
sub_df = pd.concat([sub_df, temp_df]).reset_index(drop=True)
sub_df = sub_df[(sub_df.real_training_set_size >= 20) & (sub_df.real_training_set_size <= 90)].copy()

sub_df["Trajectory Type"] = sub_df["trajectory"]

sub_df["Method"] = sub_df["obi_steps"].map(method_mapping)

g = sns.relplot(
    data=sub_df,
    x="real_training_set_size",
    y="accuracy",

sub_df = df[
    (df.obi_steps.isin([0]))
    & (df.num_samples == 10000)
    & (df.type == "Bayesian")
]
temp_df = sub_df[sub_df.obi_steps == 0].copy()
temp_df["obi_steps"] = -5
temp_df["real_training_set_size"] -= 5
sub_df = pd.concat([sub_df, temp_df]).reset_index(drop=True)
sub_df = sub_df[(sub_df.real_training_set_size >= 20) & (sub_df.real_training_set_size <= 90)].copy()

crossentropy_means = sub_df.groupby(["trajectory", "obi_steps"]).crossentropy.mean()
accuracy_means = sub_df.groupby(["trajectory", "obi_steps"]).accuracy.mean()
